Compute a = (n+1)/2 since in integer division, (n+1)/2 will give ceiling(n/2). Then b = n/2 → floor(n/2). Compute max_val = a*a + b*b

if current_count > max_val → print 'NO' and return. Else, print YES. Then proceed to build the grid. Now, building the grid:
